Text: Thank you sm.  Um, I don't necessarily feel "pain," b/c I'm numb nd don't have real human emotions anymore. I just want to acquiesce to ED like I was able to simply a few months ago.  Rationally, what you say makes perfect sense, srsly thank you. And also there's a screaming voice saying all of this is wrong, wrong wrong haha

Author: saturnplastic
Text: I think it’s important to remember your ED has nothing to do with your weight, and only your relationship with weight and food. It’s something you struggle with emotionally, that may or may not alter your physical appearance. It’s the nature of ED’s to try and make you feel invalid, but you’re just trying to get by. your pain is real.
